// Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2026-3186 — Mass File Rename (handala)
// Status: stable | Level: high | ID: 55b6509e-4449-588b-9a19-17f276a20010

#event_simpleName=*
| (FilePath = *.encrypted OR FilePath = *.locked OR FilePath = *.ransom)
| table([timestamp, ComputerName])
| limit(1000)
